cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image stylization, specifically transforming realistic photos into cartoon style images. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. The proposed method also utilizes deep neural networks (DNNs) and involves feature mapping and manipulation, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves image processing and rendering, which falls under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
